                    developed originally by Stake where players navigate
                    the grid to reveal gems while avoiding bombs.</p>
                    <a href="/Game/Rules" class="btn_1">Rules</a>
                    <a href="#" class="btn_1">Tutorial</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
